name: ForeUI Custom Library File
summary: Learn about .FCL files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: ForeUI custom libraries can be imported using the "Load Elements from .fcl File" option within the Custom Elements pane.

description: Library file created by ForeUI, a program used to create user interface mockups; saved in a compressed .ZIP format and contains .FCE files, which store custom user-made elements; used for sharing collections of custom elements.
